quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; webkitallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; mozallowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"><button class="button load_iframe_btn"><svg role="img" viewbox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" class="svgicon icon_play" height="24" stroke-linejoin="round" version="1.1" aria-hidden width="24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><polygon points="10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8"></polygon></svg> Run game</button></div></div></div><div class="donate"><a data-donate="false" class="button donate_btn" href="https://axelvejardossow.itch.io/there-is-something-in-the-anderghast-mine/purchase">Download Now</a></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><blockquote>My name is Marion, I&#x27;m 20 years old. 10 years ago, my father disappeared  without a trace. He worked at the Anderghast mine, which according to  some people, is one of the most haunted places in the world.  Some days ago, I received a letter of someone who claims to know about my  father&#x27;s whereabouts. This person is waiting for me near the Anderghast mine.  I know...it&#x27;s too suspicious...but I couldn&#x27;t ignore it. I have to know...  I have to find out what really happened to my father, even if I have to go  to that place...  I have to be careful, though. Because there&#x27;s definitely something there...  There is something in the Anderghast mine...<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1998</blockquote>  <p><br>&quot;There is Something in the Anderghast mine&quot; is an horror game created with the Rpg Maker MZ software for the 17th RPG Maker Horror Game Jam. It was made in about 19 days, so please keep in mind that there might be some bugs/typos/phasable tiles and I will (most likely) fix them (if any) after the jam ends.<br></p>  <p>Help Marion find out the truth about her father&#x27;s disappearance...and the secret of the Anderghast mine...</p>  <p></p>  <p><strong>Warning: </strong><strong><br></strong></p>  <p><strong>This game contains pixelated blood, pixelated gore, jumpscares, partial nudity, loud sounds, claustrophobia, mild language, disturbing themes, disturbing imagery, flashing lights and an oppresing atmosphere. All events, names, characters and locations are entirelyfictional and any similarity to real life is nothing but a coincidence.</strong></p>  <p></p>  <p><strong>FEATURES<br></strong></p>  <pre>  4 ENDINGS BASED ON YOUR ACTIONS AND CHOICES  </pre>  <pre>  DIFFERENT AND GRUESOME DEATH ANIMATIONS</pre>  <pre>  NIGHTMARISH, GROTESQUE AND DISTURBING SITUATIONS AND EVENTS</pre>  <pre>  OPPRESIVE, DEPRESSING AND EERIE SETTINGS</pre>  <pre>  ART GALLERY WITH UNLOCKABLE IMAGES</pre></div><div class="more_information_toggle"><div class="toggle_row"><a class="toggle_info_btn" href="javascript:void(0)">More information<svg height="6" class="svgicon icon_down_tick" role="img" width="12" version="1.1" viewbox="0 0 37 20" aria-hidden><path d="m2.0858 0c-1.1535 0-2.0858 0.86469-2.0858 1.9331 0 0.5139 0.21354 1.0183 0.38704 1.1881l18.113 16.879 18.112-16.879c0.174-0.1696 0.388-0.674 0.388-1.1879 0-1.0684-0.932-1.9331-2.086-1.9331-0.577 0-1.111 0.23008-1.49 0.57992l-14.924 13.894-14.925-13.893c-0.3777-0.34998-0.9134-0.581-1.4902-0.581z"/></svg></a></div><div class="info_panel_wrapper"><div id="game_info_panel_2894805" class